B.FO=new A.em("Rear Zero-Gravity Lounge","The rear seats recline to 148.5\xb0 \u2014 the angle at which the spine carries no load \u2014 with powered leg rests, heat, ventilation and massage. Controlled from a detachable touchscreen that lifts out of the armrest.","Rear Cabin","148.5","degrees",!0)
